markets.title: What will  say during their next earnings call?
markets.rules_primary: If Sustainability is said by any Walmart representative (including the operator of the call) during the next Walmart earnings call (including the Q+A), then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Video of the Walmart earnings call will be primarily used to resolve the market; if a consensus by Kalshi employees cannot be reached using video, transcripts of the Walmart earnings call will be used according to the news publications listed in the contract.
